{"tid":259053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心黑店！] 二手機當一手機賣！！！","createTime":"2017-05-26T15:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T02:28:40.000Z","uid":73771,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e85881bfbf23551cb4bd4458ee0b2673fd85040","tid":259053,"uid":73771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"小弟家貧 屋企人買手機都會貪平買一手既水貨 因為小弟都識少少手機上既野 如果software 有D 咩問題都多數自己搞掂唔洗搵保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老豆一年前左右係深水埗福仁某店買左部samsung s6 一買番黎我就教佢用啦 慢慢部機唔知點解越黎越多奇怪問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又無啦啦自動裝app 又自動接聽電話 開頭我都幫佢整 到前日佢話部機叉電叉得好慢 同埋叉唔到過85% 咁我就知可能係電池問題叫佢去整<br />\n<br />\n點知佢去到先達一開部機 個師傅同佢講部機係二手 比人開過 主機板同電池都唔係原裝 好明顯螺絲都鬆q曬 但我老豆自係深水埗第一次開部機 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從此以後都唔會再買水貨機 請各位買機既時候小心check 機</span></span><br />\n雖然都似係難ckeck d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f325f377e5086f8e6891d7b92e9e1f8e6b88ac23","tid":259053,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街？推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"07521f3c3984de79861be9e97f9f49babad0ce92","tid":259053,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"樓豬不孝啦買電子野都唔陪屋企人"},{"pid":"55d09694649485f15d56bc58b05b2ed39bcfaf29","tid":259053,"uid":73771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬不孝啦買電子野都唔陪屋企人</blockquote><br />\n老豆鐘意自己去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk